data.title: Earl of Athlone.
data.text:
One item.

Earl of Athlone, Prince Alexander Augustus Frederick William Alfred George Cambridge of Teck (1874-1957), Governor-General of South Africa (1924-1930).

-- The Earl of Athlone to Mrs. Enid Alexander about the part he played in mediating between Gens. Hertzog and Smuts during the SA flag crisis in 1927.
